  sectionType: 5
  title: "OYUN REHBER\u0130"
  content: "\u0130stasyonlara ula\u015Fmak i\xE7in buzlar\u0131 k\u0131rmal\u0131s\u0131n.\n\nOLU\u015ETUR:
    [E] ile kar topu yarat.\n\nB\xDCY\xDCT: Arabanla s\xFCr\xFCkleyerek topu b\xFCy\xFCt.
    \u0130lerledik\xE7e buzlar sertle\u015Fir. Zorlu\u011Fa g\xF6re topu daha da
    b\xFCy\xFCtmelisin!\n\nFIRLAT: Ni\u015Fan al ve tekrar [E]  "
